ated-posts":[{"id":15088,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/16\/sniff-water-nose-fasting\/","url_meta":{"origin":29350,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Siyam: Sniff water deep in nose unless fasting","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 16, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Laqit ibn Sabrah reported: I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, tell me about ablution.\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cPerform ablution well, clean the base of your fingers, and sniff water deep into your nose, unless you are fasting.\u201d Al-Tirmidhi said, \"The people of\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":12995,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/03\/20\/dunya-cursed-dhikr-ilm\/","url_meta":{"origin":29350,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Dunya: World is cursed except for prayer, knowledge","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 20, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIs not the world cursed and everything in it? Except for the remembrance of Allah and what facilitates it, the scholar or the student.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2322 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32706,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/07\/all-cures-but-aging\/","url_meta":{"origin":29350,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Medicine: Allah placed cures for all diseases, except aging","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 7, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Usamah ibn Sharik reported: A bedouin said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, shall we not seek treatment?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cYes, O servants of Allah, seek treatment. Verily, Allah did not place a disease but that he also placed its treatment or cure, except for one ailment.\u201d They said, \u201cO Messenger\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":29323,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/13\/prophet-not-urinate-standing\/","url_meta":{"origin":29350,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Cleanliness: The Prophet does not urinate standing up","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 13, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would not urinate unless he was sitting. Al-Tirmidhi said, \u201cThe prohibition of urinating while standing means it is a matter of etiquette and not absolute forbiddance.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 12 Grade: Jayyid (very good) according to Al-Nawawi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u062a\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13984,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/05\/anger-coal-lie-down\/","url_meta":{"origin":29350,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Anger: Son of Adam\u2019s anger is a hot coal, let him lie down","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 5, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, anger is a burning ember in the heart of the son of Adam, as you see it in the redness of his eyes and the bulging of his veins. Whoever feels anything like that,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18059,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/02\/05\/merchants-wicked-unless-fear-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":29350,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Trade: Merchants with the wicked, unless they fear Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 5, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Rifa\u2019ah ibn Rafi' reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him,\u00a0said, \u201cVerily, merchants will be raised on the Day of Resurrection with the wicked, except for those who fear Allah, behave righteously, and are truthful.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1210 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0631\u0650\u0641\u064e\u0627\u0639\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0628\u0646 \u0631\u0627\u0641\u0639\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/293